<!DOCTYPE html>
<!--配液排批规则帮助说明
	csp:dhcpha.pivas.batchruleshelp.csp
-->
<HTML XMLNS=TRAK>

<HEAD>
    <title>
        <TRAK:TRANSLATE id=title>##(%session.Get("TITLE"))##</TRAK:TRANSLATE>
    </title>
    <TRAK:HEAD>
    </TRAK:HEAD>
    <!-- Put your page Title here -->
    <HISUI/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../scripts/pharmacy/common/css/dhcpha.hisui.css">
    </script>
    <STYLE>
        /*
		.if{
			color:#017BCE;
			font-weight:bold;
			font-size:15px;
		}
		.then{
			color:#FF584C;
			font-weight:bold;
			font-size:15px;
		}
		*/
        
        .batch-title {
            color: #007ACF;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .batch-title-sign {
            height: 14px;
            margin-top: 3px;
            border-left: 5px solid #007ACF;
            float: left;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        
        div p {
            padding-top: 10px
        }
    </STYLE>
</HEAD>

<body>
    <div class="hisui-layout" fit="true" border="false">
        <div data-options="region:'center'" class="dhcpha-hisui-container">
            <div class="hisui-layout" fit="true" border="false">
                <div data-options="region:'center'" border="false" class="dhcpha-hisui-border" style="border-radius: 4px;padding:10px">
                    <div class="batch-title">
                        <div class="batch-title-sign"></div>排批算法</div>
                    <div style="border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc;padding-top:10px"></div>
                    <div style="padding-left:40px">
                        <!--p><b>以某一组液体为例</b></p-->
                        <p>A1.<span class="if">如果</span>在排批界面修改过批次，<span class="then">则</span>返回该批次,且为最终批次。</p>
                        <p>B1.<span class="if">如果</span>在用法固定批次维护中存在，<span class="then">则</span>返回该批次。</p>
                        <p>B2.<span class="if">如果</span>在药品固定批次维护中存在，<span class="then">则</span>返回该批次。</p>
                        <p>B3.<span class="if">如果</span>在时间规则维护中存在，<span class="then">则</span>返回该批次。</p>
                        <p>C1.<span class="if">以A、B</span>中返回批次为基础，<span class="then">按</span>优先级为其他规则、频次优先级、药品顺序规则记录每个病人每天每个批次每组药的液体量。</p>
                        <p>D1.<span class="if">如果</span>在容积规则维护中已存在，<span class="then">则</span>按批次顺序以及C中记录的液体量,进行批次容量累加,超出部分移动至下一批次。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="batch-title" style="margin-top:10px">
                        <div class="batch-title-sign"></div>时间规则</div>
                    <div style="border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc;padding-top:10px"></div>
                    <div style="padding-left:40px">
                        <p>按用药时间划分批次</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="batch-title" style="margin-top:10px">
                        <div class="batch-title-sign"></div>病区规则</div>
                    <div style="border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc;padding-top:10px"></div>
                    <div style="padding-left:40px">
                        <p>E1.<span class="if">如果</span>某病区已按配液中心维护，<span class="then">则</span>以该规则的明细规则为准。</p>
                        <p>E2.<span class="if">如果</span>某病区未按配液中心维护，<span class="then">则</span>以该配液中心病区为空的明细规则为准。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="batch-title" style="margin-top:10px">
                        <div class="batch-title-sign"></div>频次规则</div>
                    <div style="border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc;padding-top:10px"></div>
                    <div style="padding-left:40px">
                        <p>依据容积规则移动批次的基础，仅维护的频次可移动批次。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="batch-title" style="margin-top:10px">
                        <div class="batch-title-sign"></div>其他规则</div>
                    <div style="border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc;padding-top:10px"></div>
                    <div style="padding-left:40px">
                        <p>依据容积规则移动批次的基础，分为按持续量（用药时间顺序）、大液体量（液体量大的优先）。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
</body>

</HTML>